descriptionHtml:
Hello!
Here is my first created female human I hope you will like it.

Her name is Caitlyn - Nord race, level 1
Game starts in the moment when we choose the sign: Warrior, Mage, Thief.


Installation:

1. Go to - Documents/My games/Skyrim/saves
(If you don\'t have \"saves\" folder, create one.
2. Paste there my Game Save.
3. Play.

Feel Free to rename save name.
It was created on Polish version of the game!

Hope you will enjoy it!
author: Meritus
